::: {#hero-heading}

Welcome to the ***China Climate Communication Initiative***. 

We are a non-profit initiative committed to enhancing climate change communication in China. Our mission is to provide a transparent and accessible platform for understanding climate change perceptions within the nation. 

To this end, all our surveys, data, code, and articles are fully *open access* and *available to the public*. Explore our [studies](/projects) and join us in promoting informed discussions for a sustainable future.

:::



